gnome-screensaver: gnome-screensaver (GNOME Screen Saver)
gnome-screensaver: 
gnome-screensaver: The gnome-screensaver package contains a screen saver and locker 
gnome-screensaver: designed to have simple, sane, secure defaults and be well integrated 
gnome-screensaver: with the desktop. It supports locking down of configuration settings, has 
gnome-screensaver: translations into many languages and convenient user switching.
